caption: Great food. Still still around and doing takeout post-lockdown. Give this wonderful, family-run place some support.

I am a handroll kind of girl; I've had them from coast to coast and island to island. This place wraps up the best handrolls I've ever had. Get one of each. And add a sake. I love a sushi bar and this place does it right.
Definitely a place worth visiting, the food is great and fresh, the cost is reasonable and it is constantly well kept here. Fantastic work.
The line was long so we ordered takeout (separate menu) and had drinks on the front patio area.  Nice cardboard bento takeaway containers, good food

Aki golden dinner is a must try.
Went for the first time since pandemic rules, and it was wonderful.  The food was as good as I'd had when they were fully open, and the server as friendly and kind as ever.  I'll be returning soon.
The food and the customer service was out of sight I had the avocado and California rolls really delicious along with the chicken teriyaki plate I would definitely go there again

This place is a trip back to a simpler time when Japanese American restaurants served sashimi and sushi without all the gimmicks. When you got tempura and fried oysters and teriyaki steak and tonkatsu. Real Japanese American comfort food …

Reliable friendly service with food like the Japanese food I used to get at Japanese restaurants when I was a kid. In other words, "soul food" for my Japanese American  food craving soul.

The teriyaki sauce is just right, giving you the sweetness but not burying the protein. The sashimi salmon plated with thinly sliced lemon was a new taste but complemented nicely.

Best family owned Japanese restaurant.  I have eaten here numerous times since I was 8 years old, I'm now 50. Three generations of family members work at Aki and strive to make your meal and your dining experience like they would their own family. Definitely worth a visit.
Good food and good staff.  Repeat customer for sure.

Longtime favorite.  Family owned sushi in West LA.  Love this place, super nice staff and consistently awesome food.  Sashimi is amazing love the calamari skillet cooked.
